headline: Is Capital One Still Attractive After Its 156.7% Three Year Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Capital One Financial is still attractive after its huge run, or if the easy money has already been made, this breakdown will help you see where the value really stands today. The stock has climbed 4.5% over the last week, 27.2% year to date, and 156.7% over three years, so the market clearly sees something it likes. However, that does not automatically mean it is overpriced at $227.24. Recent headlines have focused on Capital One's push deeper into digital...
